    <comment pinned="false" h="100" w="300">MARTINGALE + RISK MANAGEMENT — runs after every contract settles.
• Loss &amp; below step cap → Stake = Stake × 1.6 (controlled progression).
• Loss &amp; step cap reached → reset Stake to base &amp; restart cycle (escalation is capped).
• Win → reset Stake to base &amp; clear loss streak (reset cycle).
• Total P&amp;L, Stop-Loss or Max-Trades hit → pause trading for the session (circuit breaker).</comment>
